PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 53 - which (a) DECLARES the severe storm which occurred in Newfoundland on September 19, 2001, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in that regard.
